But Tango is really
going to shine

00:07:06.730 --> 00:07:10.240
for a lot of entertainment
applications there.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:13.190
So those operating systems
running on our hardware

00:07:13.190 --> 00:07:16.860
platforms can support a really
wide variety of services.

00:07:16.860 --> 00:07:20.150
And they're, as I said,
the equivalent of power ups

00:07:20.150 --> 00:07:22.960
to provide that kind of
enchanting Google magic you

00:07:22.960 --> 00:07:25.000
want to put in your games.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:27.670
So for example, we've
got Google Play.

00:07:27.670 --> 00:07:31.850
The Google Play Store--
every month, Android users

00:07:31.850 --> 00:07:35.360
download more than 1.5
billion apps and games.

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:38.130
And the user ratings and
rankings on the Play Store

00:07:38.130 --> 00:07:40.817
can generate buzz to
engage your users.

00:07:40.817 --> 00:07:43.150
You can place ads for your
game right in the Play Store.

00:07:43.150 --> 00:07:45.960
And you can sell your
apps in over 190 countries

00:07:45.960 --> 00:07:47.440
and territories worldwide.

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:49.640
So tremendous reach there.

00:07:49.640 --> 00:07:52.060
And to go along with
that, Play Games Services

00:07:52.060 --> 00:07:54.480
is a really versatile
package we have that

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:56.500
helps you build better games.

00:07:56.500 --> 00:07:57.960
Just some of the
things it can do

00:07:57.960 --> 00:08:01.850
include achievements,
leaderboards, Cloud Save.

00:08:01.850 --> 00:08:04.990
It's got real time multiplayer
and quests for your mobie--

00:08:04.990 --> 00:08:08.060
and that's Android,
or iOS, and web games.

00:08:08.060 --> 00:08:10.380
