game events so that you

00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:14.500
can analyze micro-gameplay
and patterns

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:16.199
and tune your game very well.

00:08:16.199 --> 00:08:18.490
So as a designer, I find that
particularly interesting.

00:08:18.490 --> 00:08:20.950
You can get down to a very
deep level with what Play Games

00:08:20.950 --> 00:08:22.800
Services provides for you.

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:26.860
And a lot of that stuff is
very powerful and easy to use.

00:08:26.860 --> 00:08:29.460
Play Games has grown
to 450 million users

00:08:29.460 --> 00:08:31.970
since we launched it
at I/O two years ago,

00:08:31.970 --> 00:08:35.669
with 185 million users added
in just the past six months.

00:08:35.669 --> 00:08:38.309
And it's the fastest growing
mobile gaming platform

00:08:38.309 --> 00:08:39.382
in history.

