Advertising with
AdWords allows you

00:10:05.990 --> 00:10:08.210
to reach new players
at the precise moment

00:10:08.210 --> 00:10:10.050
that they're searching
for your games.

00:10:10.050 --> 00:10:12.760
And last, but
definitely not least,

