00:28:26.960 --> 00:28:32.100
And a few weeks later, average
revenue per daily active user

00:28:32.100 --> 00:28:33.590
more than doubled.

00:28:33.590 --> 00:28:39.160
And average revenue per paying
user grew by almost 70%.

00:28:39.160 --> 00:28:45.670
That's almost unheard of impact
in such a short period of time.

